ability hit him to no avail. "My body is immune to these attacks. Ive known 
this since the last time I met you. I think you have a problem." He 
transformed into Optimus Prime and fired the mega gun at Empath.
Destructor  threw a spark seeking bomb to Windlord and shot two plasma shots 
at him.
